org.wso2.transport.http.netty.sender.http2

Interface Http2DataEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RedirectHandler, TimeoutHandler

    public interface Http2DataEventListener
    Http2DataEventListener represents a data listener for http2 data transfer events.
